                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.71212/66: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Coolidge</persName> to
                        President <persName type="to">Calles</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-10-01T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 1, 1928—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Upon the occasion of the inauguration of the air mail service between this
                    country and Mexico, it gives me great pleasure to express to you my
                    felicitations on this important step in the advancement of the communication
                    between our two countries, which will become a new bond in bringing together
                    more closely the relations between Mexico and the United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Calvin Coolidge</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
